    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Credibility assessment formally accepted as a complete package for regulatory submission purposes. Note: the overall simulation credibility for the VAD COU is not accepted — all 7 assessed factors fall below required levels and 6 factors remain as epistemic gaps. The assessment package itself is accepted as accurately representing the current state of evidence. Provenance for some validation results was not fully captured in structured form; experimental campaigns were performed but activity records are incomplete for operating points 3, 4, and the Monte Carlo envelope result.",
